      "text": "So, let's talk about it later."
    },
    {
      "start": 206.52,
      "end": 206.78,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 206.86,
      "end": 211.82,
      "text": "영화에 대해서 구체적인 내용은 우리가 차차 회를 거듭하면서 할 거고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 211.9,
      "end": 212.68,
      "text": "차차, 작은 작은."
    },
    {
      "start": 212.84,
      "end": 214.84,
      "text": "네, 첫 장면 먼저 듣고 오겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 216.0,
      "end": 219.14,
      "text": "With my fortune comes a great responsibility."
    },
    {
      "start": 220.4,
      "end": 225.98,
      "text": "You must be willing and able to take care of my loyal companion, Trouble."
    },
    {
      "start": 226.54,
      "end": 227.18,
      "text": "Trouble?"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.9,
      "end": 228.64,
      "text": "Who's in trouble?"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.42,
      "end": 229.9,
      "text": "No one."
    },
    {
      "start": 230.3,
      "end": 231.32,
      "text": "Trouble is the dog."
    },
    {
      "start": 231.92,
      "end": 233.88,
      "text": "Who cares about the dog?"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.2,
      "end": 234.72,
      "text": "You do."
