    {
      "start": 276.75,
      "end": 277.07,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 277.29,
      "end": 277.93,
      "text": "개팔자."
    },
    {
      "start": 278.37,
      "end": 278.97,
      "text": "상팔자."
    },
    {
      "start": 279.71,
      "end": 280.55,
      "text": "Yeah, 그런 말이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 280.77,
      "end": 281.49,
      "text": "딱 그겁니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 281.75,
      "end": 289.33,
      "text": "그래서 이 Trouble이라는 강아지가 has lived under the top-notch, 이렇게 표현할 수 있지 않을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.33,
      "end": 291.41,
      "text": "He has a top-notch lifestyle."
    },
    {
      "start": 291.61,
      "end": 292.57,
      "text": "Yeah, care."
    },
    {
      "start": 292.93,
      "end": 293.33,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.43,
      "end": 293.89,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.91,
      "end": 297.53,
      "text": "He gets top-of-the-line care, top-of-the-line treatment."
    },
    {
      "start": 297.65,
      "end": 297.85,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 297.97,
      "end": 298.59,
      "text": "Better than me."
    },
    {
      "start": 298.77,
      "end": 304.33,
      "text": "And always surrounded by so many people, such as steward, 집사도 있었잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 304.49,
      "end": 305.21,
      "text": "He has a butler."
    },
    {
      "start": 305.33,
      "end": 305.71,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 305.71,
      "end": 306.75,
      "text": "He has a masseuse."
    },
    {
      "start": 306.85,
      "end": 308.61,
      "text": "He has someone to make him happy."
