    {
      "start": 311.71,
      "end": 311.95,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 312.19,
      "end": 313.25,
      "text": "A dog therapist."
    },
    {
      "start": 313.25,
      "end": 317.47,
      "text": "정말 perfect한 그런 환경에서 자라고 있었던 강아지입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 317.47,
      "end": 318.53,
      "text": "I don't even have a therapist."
    },
    {
      "start": 318.53,
      "end": 320.33,
      "text": "I don't have most of those things."
    },
    {
      "start": 320.57,
      "end": 321.17,
      "text": "I'm jealous."
    },
    {
      "start": 321.43,
      "end": 324.09,
      "text": "저도 되게 jealous해지는 그런 장면이었는데."
    },
    {
      "start": 324.17,
      "end": 325.91,
      "text": "But suddenly, something happens."
    },
    {
      "start": 325.99,
      "end": 326.59,
      "text": "그렇죠, 그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 326.79,
      "end": 329.63,
      "text": "무엇보다 이 주인인 할머니가 있는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 329.95,
      "end": 332.45,
      "text": "아주 무한 사랑을 해줬던 할머니인데."
    },
    {
      "start": 333.49,
      "end": 337.51,
      "text": "그 Trouble의 할머니가 was gone and passed away one day."
    },
    {
      "start": 337.65,
      "end": 338.67,
      "text": "She passed away suddenly."
    },
    {
      "start": 338.71,
      "end": 339.01,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 339.63,
      "end": 343.51,
      "text": "그리고 나서는 he's put in an extremely different situation."
    },
    {
      "start": 343.69,
      "end": 344.07,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 344.25,
      "end": 346.13,
      "text": "완전 다른 상황에 놓이게 되었잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 346.13,
      "end": 347.91,
      "text": "There's nobody to take care of him."
    },
    {
      "start": 347.91,
      "end": 348.97,
      "text": "and pamper him."
    },
    {
      "start": 349.09,
      "end": 349.91,
      "text": "네, 진짜."
    },
    {
      "start": 349.91,
      "end": 354.37,
      "text": "And those niece and nephew of the old lady who passed away,"
    },
    {
      "start": 354.45,
      "end": 359.79,
      "text": "they come to the mansion and they don't really care about,"
    },
    {
      "start": 359.95,
      "end": 360.55,
      "text": "oh, she died."
    },
    {
      "start": 360.59,
      "end": 360.89,
      "text": "맞아요."
