    {
      "start": 711.31,
      "end": 712.65,
      "text": "벌써부터 궁금해집니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 712.77,
      "end": 712.99,
      "text": "그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 713.69,
      "end": 715.21,
      "text": "이 내용 한 번 더 들어보시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 715.55,
      "end": 717.16,
      "text": "With my fortune"
    },
    {
      "start": 717.16,
      "end": 719.2,
      "text": "comes a great responsibility."
    },
    {
      "start": 720.48,
      "end": 721.56,
      "text": "You must be willing"
    },
    {
      "start": 721.56,
      "end": 722.58,
      "text": "and able"
    },
    {
      "start": 722.58,
      "end": 725.06,
      "text": "to take care of my loyal companion"
    },
    {
      "start": 725.06,
      "end": 726.06,
      "text": "Trouble."
    },
    {
      "start": 726.06,
      "end": 727.24,
      "text": "Trouble?"
    },
    {
      "start": 727.7,
      "end": 728.7,
      "text": "Who's in trouble?"
    },
    {
      "start": 729.48,
      "end": 729.96,
      "text": "No one."
    },
    {
      "start": 730.38,
      "end": 731.36,
      "text": "Trouble is the dog."
    },
    {
      "start": 732.16,
      "end": 733.94,
      "text": "Who cares about the dog?"
    },
    {
      "start": 734.24,
      "end": 734.8,
      "text": "You do."
    },
    {
      "start": 735.34,
      "end": 736.66,
      "text": "He's in your care."
    },
    {
      "start": 736.78,
      "end": 737.34,
      "text": "Oh no."
    },
    {
      "start": 737.76,
      "end": 739.24,
      "text": "No no no no no no no no no no."
    },
    {
      "start": 739.24,
      "end": 741.58,
      "text": "I am not a dog person."
    },
    {
      "start": 741.78,
      "end": 742.1,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "start": 742.94,
      "end": 743.86,
      "text": "Then I'm afraid"
    },
    {
      "start": 743.86,
      "end": 745.24,
      "text": "you forfeit the rights"
    },
    {
      "start": 745.24,
      "end": 746.58,
      "text": "to the entire fortune."
    },
    {
      "start": 746.58,
      "end": 749.52,
      "text": "네 저는 이 초반에"
    },
    {
      "start": 749.52,
      "end": 750.48,
      "text": "Mrs. Fender"
    },
    {
      "start": 750.48,
      "end": 751.42,
      "text": "그 할머니가"
    },
    {
      "start": 751.42,
      "end": 752.76,
      "text": "이야기하신 말씀이"
    },
    {
      "start": 752.76,
      "end": 754.4,
      "text": "right하다고 생각해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 754.5,
      "end": 755.74,
      "text": "정말 옳은 말씀입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 756.16,
      "end": 756.64,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 756.78,
      "end": 757.88,
      "text": "There's a big responsibility"
    },
    {
      "start": 757.88,
      "end": 759.08,
      "text": "to raise dogs."
    },
    {
      "start": 759.3,
      "end": 759.82,
      "text": "Sure."
    },
    {
      "start": 760.16,
      "end": 760.18,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 760.24,
      "end": 761.44,
      "text": "아주 중요한 메시지죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 761.96,
      "end": 762.32,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 762.58,
      "end": 764.02,
      "text": "This money is not for free."
    },
    {
      "start": 764.16,
      "end": 765.46,
      "text": "You're gonna have to raise"
    },
    {
      "start": 765.46,
      "end": 766.3,
      "text": "my trouble."
    },
    {
      "start": 766.44,
      "end": 766.66,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 766.66,
      "end": 767.32,
      "text": "My darling."
    },
    {
      "start": 767.32,
      "end": 768.16,
      "text": "My precious."
    },
    {
      "start": 768.26,
      "end": 768.46,
      "text": "Anyway,"
    },
    {
      "start": 768.58,
      "end": 769.76,
      "text": "where's the dog trouble now?"
    },
    {
      "start": 770.44,
      "end": 771.18,
      "text": "Where did he go?"
    },
    {
      "start": 771.18,
      "end": 772.92,
      "text": "He was in a big truck"
    },
    {
      "start": 772.92,
      "end": 774.66,
      "text": "and moved to somewhere."
    },
    {
      "start": 774.96,
      "end": 775.64,
      "text": "아,"
    },
    {
      "start": 775.82,
      "end": 777.14,
      "text": "어디로 가고 있는 것인지"
    },
    {
      "start": 777.14,
      "end": 778.48,
      "text": "굉장히 궁금증을"
    },
    {
      "start": 778.48,
      "end": 779.76,
      "text": "유발하던 장면이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 779.8,
      "end": 780.92,
      "text": "I felt sorry for him."
    },
    {
      "start": 781.1,
      "end": 782.6,
      "text": "Even while he was moving"
    },
    {
      "start": 782.6,
      "end": 783.52,
      "text": "in that truck,"
    },
    {
      "start": 783.86,
      "end": 784.88,
      "text": "he didn't even know"
    },
    {
      "start": 784.88,
      "end": 786.1,
      "text": "that his owner"
    },
    {
      "start": 786.1,
      "end": 787.08,
      "text": "had passed away."
    },
    {
      "start": 787.14,
      "end": 787.46,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 787.7,
      "end": 788.72,
      "text": "He saw her picture"
    },
    {
      "start": 788.72,
      "end": 789.88,
      "text": "and her hat."
    },
    {
      "start": 790.12,
      "end": 791.16,
      "text": "Where is she?"
    },
    {
      "start": 791.16,
      "end": 791.9,
      "text": "어디 갔지?"
    },
    {
      "start": 791.98,
      "end": 793.06,
      "text": "할머니가 좋아하는 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 793.06,
      "end": 793.82,
      "text": "여기 다 있는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 793.82,
      "end": 796.16,
      "text": "왜 할머니는 안 계시지?"
    },
    {
      "start": 796.28,
      "end": 797.5,
      "text": "라고 두리번거렸던"
    },
    {
      "start": 797.5,
      "end": 798.54,
      "text": "장면이 기억이 납니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 799.52,
      "end": 800.6,
      "text": "김선호님께서"
    },
    {
      "start": 800.6,
      "end": 802.74,
      "text": "크리스 내 공주님들"
    },
    {
      "start": 802.74,
      "end": 804.3,
      "text": "영어는 좀 늘었나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 804.66,
      "end": 805.86,
      "text": "질문해 주셨어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 806.18,
      "end": 807.32,
      "text": "That's a good question."
    },
    {
      "start": 807.52,
      "end": 807.56,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 808.04,
      "end": 808.32,
      "text": "Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 808.44,
      "end": 809.22,
      "text": "they understand"
    },
    {
      "start": 809.22,
      "end": 810.0,
      "text": "a lot of English."
    },
    {
      "start": 810.12,
      "end": 810.58,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 810.88,
      "end": 811.56,
      "text": "My youngest"
    },
    {
      "start": 811.56,
      "end": 812.48,
      "text": "actually speaks"
    },
    {
      "start": 812.48,
      "end": 813.1,
      "text": "more English."
    },
    {
      "start": 813.3,
      "end": 813.64,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 814.04,
      "end": 814.34,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 814.64,
      "end": 816.0,
      "text": "I think she likes languages."
    },
    {
      "start": 816.18,
      "end": 816.36,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 816.54,
      "end": 817.38,
      "text": "So she's always,"
    },
    {
      "start": 817.38,
      "end": 818.78,
      "text": "she carries this pen around"
    },
    {
      "start": 818.78,
      "end": 820.32,
      "text": "that speaks English to her."
    },
    {
      "start": 820.46,
      "end": 820.9,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 821.06,
      "end": 821.86,
      "text": "That's good news."
    },
    {
      "start": 821.88,
      "end": 822.96,
      "text": "And she brags to dad."
    },
    {
      "start": 823.02,
      "end": 823.66,
      "text": "Daddy, daddy."
    },
    {
      "start": 823.86,
      "end": 824.8,
      "text": "I can read this."
    },
    {
      "start": 824.86,
      "end": 826.38,
      "text": "정말 adorable 한 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 826.5,
      "end": 827.16,
      "text": "They're getting better."
    },
    {
      "start": 827.38,
      "end": 829.42,
      "text": "특히 이 4월의 영화가"
    },
    {
      "start": 829.42,
      "end": 830.66,
      "text": "애니메이션이잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 830.76,
      "end": 832.44,
      "text": "귀여운 댕댕이 영화이니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 832.44,
      "end": 834.54,
      "text": "우리 어린 친구들이"
    },
    {
      "start": 834.54,
      "end": 835.3,
      "text": "함께 들어도"
    },
    {
      "start": 835.3,
      "end": 836.3,
      "text": "정말 재미있게"
    },
    {
      "start": 836.3,
      "end": 837.44,
      "text": "잘 들을 수 있을 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 837.56,
      "end": 837.78,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 837.88,
      "end": 839.0,
      "text": "I watched this with my daughters."
    },
    {
      "start": 839.26,
      "end": 840.54,
      "text": "They liked it a lot."
    },
    {
      "start": 840.68,
      "end": 841.02,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 841.22,
      "end": 843.0,
      "text": "Very enjoyable for the whole family."
    },
    {
      "start": 843.2,
      "end": 843.42,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 843.66,
      "end": 844.74,
      "text": "아주 기쁜 소식입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 845.24,
      "end": 846.36,
      "text": "우린 다음 주에"
    },
    {
      "start": 846.36,
      "end": 847.0,
      "text": "이어갈게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 847.28,
      "end": 848.06,
      "text": "I'll see you next week."
    }
  ]
}